Trinity::

She looked around and jumped down to the ground. She walks over and 
sees a dimembered torso of a bot.  She nudges the shoulder and paws 
at it.  She then lowers her head and starts to cry. "Mom."  she 
whines and looks around.  She then sees a head of another bot a few 
feet away and walks up to it.  She looks at it and keeps 
crying. "Dad."  She layed on the ground next to the head and lowers 
her head onto her front paws and cries.
